[[!tag Energy_Drink Review]]

Bang is my go-to brand when I want a zero-sugar + high-caffeine energy drink,
particularly useful when I'd rather not drink my calories. The flavors are
reliable and there are so, so many of them. Most of them taste like candy.
Unfortunately the drinks [no longer contain Super
Creatine](https://www.foodbev.com/news/monster-secures-311m-victory-over-bang-energy-in-false-advertising-case),
but it's not like Super Creatine had effects similar to creatine in the first
place. Fatal mistake! I talked a bit about Super Creatine also in the first Bang
review on this site, [[Bang_Black_Cherry_Vanilla]].

