The taste of Cotton Candy is hollow up front, eventually dissolving into an
empty, vapid approximation of waxy, gummy candy. Last, you taste a light note of
citric acid. It doesn't really taste like cotton candy in particular but the
taste is still very good. It's one of my favorite Bang flavors for that reason.

